virtual AvrcpResponse BtAvrcpCommandInterface::OnAvrcpCommand (  AvrcpCommand  cmd  )  const [pure virtual]
 

Plugin applications which inherit this class should implement this function. This function is invoked by MMI Panel application on receiving BT Apoxi notification. It is assumed that the method would return immediately.
